articles.author: David Rising
articles.title: Ukraine downs Russian hypersonic missile with US Patriot - The Associated Press
articles.description: Ukraine’s air force claims to have downed a Russian hypersonic missile over Kyiv using newly acquired American Patriot defense systems, the first known time the country has been able to intercept one of Moscow’s most modern missiles.
